author: Jorge Alonso
title: Watch Ezekiel Elliott Chase Down And Tackle Fan Who Ran Onto The Field At The Pro Bowl
text:
Cowboys running back Ezekiel Elliot is a beast on offense but he might have to consider playing some defense next season.
During tonight’s Pro Bowl, Zeke showcased his speed after he chased down this one fan who ran onto the field. 
@EzekielElliott @DezBryant got the man running on the field !! pic.twitter.com/1pgKQUKpV9 
— cøle (@coIenerad) January 30, 2017
